trailingComments.value: IE does not support the download attribute on the links. In this case, trigger opening of the link in
a new window, in order to prevent navigating away from the page. This might collide with the popup
blocker, but at least it can be configured on the client side.
Do this also in case `AttachmentDownloadType` is set to inline.
